Complaints_Final Jansen Baier 5/6/2022

This website explores consumer complaints against US Banks in the year 2020. Specifically, it explores the most common complaints against the most complained banks, using the states to further analyze this data. The first chart shows the most complaints per state specifically for the top three most complained companies. The next chart explores the top three complaints by each state, with different colors showing each complaint.

Following the two charts are two tables. The first table explores how many complaints each of the top 10 companies by complaints received. The next chart explores the top 5 complaints of the top 5 companies by complaints.

The only major caveat to consider in this data is that date from outlying minor US islands was the remove because it had little data and it was altering the framing of other graphs in this project beyond the point of readability.
